I had such an amazing experience with @valmartsx not only was I satisfied with how professional she is but the results!? She came through !!! I’ve gotten this treatment done before  but NEVER had rapid results like this. Definitely will be doing more sessions. 

Service provided was “WAISTED”+ BBL Waisted package consists of 4 services with an extra free service. 

Endermolie 
Wood therapy 
Cavitation 
Lymphatic massage 
+skin tightening.
Follow  @valmartsx and hit her up for services if you’re in Miami or coming to Miami ! You won’t be disappointed.
